                        <interp inst="t18490820-name-189" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE LANGDON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, N</hi> 265). I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">read—<persName id="t18490820-name-190">
                        <interp inst="t18490820-name-190" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490820-name-190" type="surname" value="HARDEN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490820-name-190" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>John Harden</persName> convicted Dec</hi>, 1847, <hi rend="italic">and confined one year</hi>)—I was present at the trial—Evans is the person.</p>
